    "Details": "The PX-FR is the fire and rescue kit. A Sprayer in the left arm draws from a one-ton Liquid Storage Tank fed by a Light Fluid Suction System for refilling in flooded areas. A Hatchet in the right arm breaks through debris to reach trapped civilians. Paramedic Equipment and a half-ton Cargo Bay enable casualty transport. A Searchlight aids visibility in dark or smoke-filled environments.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.97</color></b>",
